### ============================================
### UPDATE PROFILE TESTS
### ============================================

### 9. Update Profile - JUST BIO (should succeed)
PATCH {{userUrl}}/profile
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "bio": "Updated my bio!"
}

### 10. Get Profile (verify bio update)
GET {{userUrl}}/me
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 11. Update Profile - MULTIPLE BASIC FIELDS
PATCH {{userUrl}}/profile
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "John Updated Doe",
  "age": 25,
  "bio": "Updated again with new age"
}

### 12. Update Profile - JUST USERNAME
PATCH {{userUrl}}/profile
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "newusername123"
}

### 13. Update Profile - LOCATION & BUDGET
PATCH {{userUrl}}/profile
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "location": "Rabat",
  "budget": 6000,
  "currency": "EUR"
}

